The paper discusses the specification, programming, and verification of distributed systems, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also focuses on different programming languages and their design choices, syntax, and semantics, which relates to Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). The paper also mentions verification techniques, which falls under Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
